<Game>
	<Name>Castle of Illusion Starring Mickey Mouse (USA, Europe)</Name>
	<plot>The search is on! Mickey is on the trail of a wicked Witch named Mizrabel, who has kidnapped Minnie. Mickey must find seven gems to save Minnie. Run, leap and bounce with Mickey, slinging apples and marbles at enemies. Then, get ready to challenge your most dangerous foe, Witch Mizrabel herself!Cheat: Extra Life After Evert LevelWhen you finish a level, when the end-of-level screen (where your bonus points are added up) appears, press Start rapidly until you hear a ringing sound. You now have one more life than before. </plot>
